                    </div>
                    <span>There is no magic bullit or mystical secret to achieving wealth in our society today. It has never been easier than it is today nor has there ever been more mis-information to make it seem harder than it really is.  There is a proven step-by-step approach and David Bach has absolutely nailed it.  Don't fall for get rich quick or other gimmicks by self-proclaimed gurus.
<br />
<br />David's book was a great affirmation for me to know I am on the right track.  I will recommend this book to several of my friends and loved ones who feel overwhelmed and stressed by where they are in relation to where they want to be.  Thank you David!   </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">I'm so excited! This is better than a trashy novel!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>6</span>
                      /
                      <span>13</span>
                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2005-03-08</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>The trouble with most people nowadays is they are looking for a SEXY way of getting rich! They want it fast and big! Well, the road to riches requires discipline and work for most people. That is the boring truth. If nothing else, the numbers that David Bach offers as proof that this system works is worth reading the book. Heck, even if you have to go to the library and check it out...do it! Read it! Start early! Time is the most important tool in the whole plan. If you save/invest now, WHILE you are paying off your debts, you will be so far ahead. 
<br />
<br />Trust me! The price of this book was worth it to me! I saw Bach on Oprah and was amazed at the trouble some of those folks were in. Trouble is, most Americans are in such debt that they have given up! Did I call my creditors and get my interest rates lowered ten years ago? YES!! They will work with you as long as you talk to them in nice, polite tones. It took a while to get out of debt but I did it. 
<br />
<br />Now I am HOT to invest!!! I told my husband this book is better than porno! He laughed! He has been applying these principles for years and his investment in savings thirty years ago multiplied 8...yes 8 times! He invested in boring things, good solid companies, real estate, just like David Bach writes. But I needed to see it on the written page to "get it". At age 50, I am new to this game and am doing this with my own money. I am starting late but I know I will have millions for retirement of my own money. 
<br />
<br />Check the book out from the library for a trial run, or go to the big book store with the comfy chairs and read for a while.....you'll probably end up owning this book before it is all said and done! It was a marvelous investment in my life. I have been telling every woman, young and older about it!
<br />
<br /></span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Solid advice for any age</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
